headline: Getting a Tax Refund? 3 Energy Stocks to Buy With Your Refund Check.
summary: One place to consider putting that money is the energy sector, which offers the potential to earn income and grow the value of your tax refund.  Enbridge (NYSE: ENB), NextEra Energy (NYSE: NEE), and Kinder Morgan (NYSE: KMI) stand out to a few Fool.com contributors as excellent energy stocks to consider buying with your tax refund (or any other source of cash you have available to invest).  Reuben Gregg Brewer (Enbridge): There are two big dividend numbers when it comes to Canadian midstream giant Enbridge.
